-- South African Fire Kills 18 in Old Age Home, 84 Others Rescued, Sapa Says
-- Vernon Wessels
-- 2010-08-02T05:02:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-02/south-african-fire-kills-18-in-old-age-home-84-others-rescued-sapa-says.html

          
          
             Eighteen people died after a fire
broke out in an old-age home near Johannesburg, the South
African Press Association said, citing Chris Botha, a spokesman
for Netcare911.  
 Another 84 people rescued from the fire were taken to a
nearby church, the Johannesburg-based news service said.  
          
          


  


        